# Template for .server.env -- copy to the CLONE ROOT on the VPS as `.server.env`
# ONLY if your layout differs from the default. Git-ignored: stays on the VPS.
#
# tools/server-update.sh defaults WEBROOT to /var/www/ota/public, so on a
# standard deploy you don't need this file at all. Create it only to override.
WEBROOT=/var/www/ota/public
